                            <comment id="10767" author="juergen.hoeller" created="Thu, 12 Aug 2004 01:35:27 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks for reporting this - I&apos;ve just fixed AbstractBeanFactory&apos;s &quot;getSingletonNames&quot; implementation to properly synchronize on the singletonCache Map.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;BTW, regarding your code example: You don&apos;t need to call getBean for each name returned by getBeansOfType. The latter returns a Map with bean names as keys and bean instances as values, so I recommend to simply fetch the bean instances from the Map.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Juergen&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
